## Dataset

The dataset used in this project is the **Face Mask Detection Dataset** available on Kaggle.

**Source:** Kaggle  
**Dataset Link:** https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/omkargurav/face-mask-dataset/data?select=data

### Description
This dataset contains images of people with and without face masks. It is commonly used for training computer vision models for face mask detection tasks.

### Classes
The dataset contains two main categories:
- **With Mask**
- **Without Mask**

### Dataset Usage in this Project
In this project, the dataset is used to train and evaluate deep learning models for detecting whether a person is wearing a face mask.


